Today is #worldmentalhealthday ... If you are one of the thousands dealing with internal battles...I am with you. I commend you for fighting behind closed doors, for recognizing your strength, and admitting that it's okay to not always be okay. We have come so far in understanding mental illness, but have a ways to go. Here is to a more understanding and nonjudgmental future ⭐️ and remember to always water what's on the inside too 💐
